I still remember the first time i heard this song in 2019 in radio🙂 Fell in love with this song. Recorded the song and listened hundreds of time. Then ... Forgot about it..
Today after 6 years, i came back. Now I'm 23. So many things has changed now.. felt a bit emotional thinking how that 17 yr old girl used think about her.. she loved herself and had so much hope about love and life..
And now.. everything has become harsh !....
